    Method new()

    Create a new FraudsterClient object

    Usage

    FraudsterClient$new(locale = NULL)

    Arguments

    locale

    (character) the locale to use. options: en_US (default), fr_FR, fr_CH, hr_FR, fa_IR, pl_PL, ru_RU, uk_UA, zh_TW.

    Returns

    A new RequestSignature object
